INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('377', '1', '2016-11-03 10:29:33', '2016-11-03 10:29:33', '<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /> </a>\r\n<h5><a href=\"#\">Bankruptcy Law</a></h5>\r\nBankruptcy is a legal status of a person or other entity that cannot repay the debts it owes to creditors.\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /> </a>\r\n<h5><a href=\"#\">Civil Rights Law</a></h5>\r\nThey ensure one\'s ability to participate in the civil and political life of the society and state without discrimination.\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /> </a>\r\n<h5><a href=\"#\">Corporate Law</a></h5>\r\nCorporate law is the practice or study of how shareholders, directors, creditors and others, interact with one another.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /> </a>\r\n<h5><a href=\"#\">Criminal Law</a></h5>\r\nIt regulates social conduct and proscribes whatever is threatening, harmful to the health and safety of people.\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /> </a>\r\n<h5><a href=\"#\">Family Unit Law</a></h5>\r\nMarriage can be recognized by a state, an organization, a religious authority, a tribal group, a local community or peers.\r\n<a href=\"#\">\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" /> </a>\r\n<h5><a href=\"#\">Personal Injury Law</a></h5>\r\nA personal injury lawyer is responsible for interviewing prospective clients and evaluating their cases.', 'Oblasti delovanja', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'oblasti-delovanja', '', '', '2017-11-14 21:11:35', '2017-11-14 20:11:35', '', '0', 'http://localhost:8888/startright/?page_id=377', '0', 'page', '', '0');
