INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('1138', '1', '2016-11-03 13:10:13', '2016-11-03 13:10:13', '<p>Civil and political rights are a class of rights that protect individuals\' freedom from infringement by governments, social organizations, and private individuals. They ensure one\'s ability to participate in the civil and political life of the society and state without discrimination.</p><p>Civil rights include the ensuring of peoples\' physical and mental integrity, life, and safety; protection from discrimination on grounds such as race, gender, national origin, colour, age, political affiliation, ethnicity, religion, or disability; and individual rights such as privacy and the freedoms of thought, speech, religion, press, assembly, and movement. Political rights include natural justice (procedural fairness) in law, such as the rights of the accused, including the right to a fair trial; due process; the right to seek redress or a legal remedy; and rights of participation in civil society and politics.</p>		\n		<img width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" src=\"http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" />		\n		<img width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" src=\"http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeho