alt=\"placeholder_400_400\" />\n													Brian Harrison\n													Engineer\n		<h2>Work with the best</h2><p>Our success as a firm has been built on a clear client-focused strategy, a commitment to excellence and the calibre of our world-class people.</p>		\n			<a href=\"#\">\n						Get in touch with us\n					</a>\n		', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1126-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-08 12:27:05', '2017-11-08 11:27:05', '', '1126', 'http://krasa.dev/2017/11/08/1126-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
