INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('1219', '1', '2017-11-17 12:05:41', '2017-11-17 11:05:41', 'Corporate law (also \"company\" or \"corporations\" law) is the practice or study of how shareholders, directors, employees, creditors, and other stakeholders such as consumers, the community, and the environment interact with one another.\r\n\r\nCorporate law is a part of a broader companies law (or law of business associations). Other types of business associations can include partnerships (in the UK governed by the Partnership Act 1890), or trusts (like a pension fund), or companies limited by guarantee (like some community organizations or charities).\r\n\r\nUnder law, corporations of all sizes have separate legal personality, with limited or unlimited liability for its shareholders. They control the company through a board of directors which, in turn, typically delegates control of the corporation\'s day-to-day operations to a full-time executive.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" />\r\n<img src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720.png 1080w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-300x200.png 300w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-768x512.png 768w, http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/02/placeholder_1080_720-1024x683.png 1024w\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" />\r\n<h4>Why Choose Us</h4>\r\nExpertise\r\nExperience Highlights\r\nAccolades\r\nExpertise\r\n\r\nOur group has been ranked by the Williamson Fund Report, the leading independent industry survey, as the leading practice by assets under management for the fifth year in a row.\r\n\r\nExperience Highlights\r\n\r\nRepresentative experience of the group includes:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bank loan funds using section subsidiaries for several large international investment managers, including a hybrid fund and CLO structure.</li>\r\n 	<li>The launch of a wide range of UCITS products including traditional long only equity, bond and money market funds.</li>\r\n 	<li>Acting for over half of the domiciled money market funds by AUM, with industry leading experience in innovative areas and accumulation share classes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAccolades\r\n\r\nThis firm is the gold standard amongst a choice of providers. The lawyers are knowledgeable and always know what is coming down the line.\"\r\n<h6>Jefferson United States</h6>', 'Privredno pravo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '414-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-17 12:05:41', '2017-11-17 11:05:41', '', '414', 'http://krasa.dev/2017/11/17/414-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
