p-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0008-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0008-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0008-300x200.jpg 300w, http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0008-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\" />				</a>\n		<h5><a href=\"/privredno-pravo\">Privredno pravo</a></h5><p>Kancelarija J&amp;K zastupa više privrednih društava, kako domaćih tako i stranih. </p>		\n		<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Iskustvo</h5><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Preko 10 godina iskustva<br /></p>		\n		<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Energija</h5><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Mlad i energičan tim<br /></p>		\n		<h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">Profesionalizam</h5><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Rezultati u prvom planu<br /></p><h3>Naši klijenti su prioritet našeg rada</h3><p>Naše glavne osobine su talenat, rezultati, izvrsnost, fokus na klijentima, timski rad i one nam omogućavaju da postižemo najviše standarde kao profesionalni advokati.</p>		\n		<img width=\"760\" height=\"479\" src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0098-1024x645.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0098-1024x645.jpg 1024w, http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0098-300x189.jpg 300w, http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0098-768x484.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\" />		\n		<img width=\"760\" height=\"507\" src=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0018-1-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0018-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0018-1-300x200.jpg 300w, http://krasa.dev/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/EXPO-0018-1-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\" />		\n		<h3>Vaše zadovoljstvo nam je ključno</h3><p>Inovativnost, napredak, prilagodljivost različitim situacijama i razumevanje potreba klijenata nam omogućavaju da postižemo izuzetne rezultate.</p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Client Testimonials</h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Since 1986, we’ve worked extremely hard to make a positive difference in the lives of people from all walks of life. We are proud of the feedback we receive regarding the quality of our work and commitment to our clients.</p>		\n							Focused, determined, and always dedicated to achieving the best results. This firm has excellent knowledge of the law, and is firmly dedicated to meticulous preparation of  cases.\n							<img src=\"http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/01/placeholder_400_400.png\" alt=\"placeholder_400_400\" />\n													Patricia Redmond\n													Architect\n							This is one of the best law firms in the United States. I have worked with them on several complex matters and have been impressed each and every time by their professionalism and knowledge.\n							<img src=\"http://themedemo.createandcode.com/judgementdata/wp-content/uploads/sites/24/2017/01/placeholder_400_400.png\" alt=\"placeholder_400_400\" />\n													Brian Harrison\n													Engineer\n		<h2>Radite sa najboljima</h2><p>Naš uspeh je izgrađen na strategiji fokusa na klijente, posvećenosti i izuzetnom kadru.</p>		\n			<a href=\"/kontakt\">\n						Kontaktirajte nas\n					</a>\n		', 'Početna', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1126-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-11-17 13:35:10', '2017-11-17 12:35:10', '', '1126', 'http://krasa.dev/2017/11/17/1126-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
